/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
   LAYER NAVIGATION
‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
function showLayer(id) {
    document.querySelectorAll('.layer').forEach(l => l.classList.remove('active'));
    document.getElementById(id).classList.add('active');
    currentLayer = id;
    window.scrollTo(0, 0);

    const aiBtn = document.getElementById('aiAssistantBtn');
    const loggedInLayers = ['dashboardLayer','tradingLayer','depositLayer','withdrawalLayer','botsLayer','historyLayer','referralLayer','profileLayer'];
    if (aiBtn) aiBtn.style.display = loggedInLayers.includes(id) ? 'block' : 'none';

    loadChartsForLayer(id);

    if (id === 'dashboardLayer') updateDashboard();
    if (id === 'tradingLayer') {
        updateOrderBook();
        setEl('tradeAvailableBalance', '$' + (currentAccountMode === 'demo' ? (currentUser?.demoBalance || 0) : (currentUser?.realBalance || 0)).toFixed(2));
    }
    if (id === 'withdrawalLayer') updateWithdrawalPage();
    if (id === 'referralLayer') updateReferralPage();
    if (id === 'historyLayer') generateTradeHistory();
    if (id === 'profileLayer') populateProfileForm();
}

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
   ACCOUNT MODE
‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
function switchAccount(mode) {
    currentAccountMode = mode;
    const demoBtn = document.getElementById('switchToDemo');
    const realBtn = document.getElementById('switchToReal');
    const indicator = document.getElementById('accountModeIndicator');

    if (mode === 'demo') {
        demoBtn.classList.add('active'); realBtn.classList.remove('active');
        if (indicator) indicator.innerHTML = `<div style="background:rgba(14,203,129,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(14,203,129,0.2);border-radius:10px;padding:10px 16px;font-size:13px;color:var(--accent-green);font-weight:600;">üìä Demo Mode ‚Äî Practice with virtual funds. No real money at risk.</div>`;
    } else {
        realBtn.classList.add('active'); demoBtn.classList.remove('active');
        if (indicator) indicator.innerHTML = `<div style="background:rgba(246,70,93,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(246,70,93,0.2);border-radius:10px;padding:10px 16px;font-size:13px;color:var(--accent-red);font-weight:600;">üíé Real Mode ‚Äî Live funds. All profits & losses are real.</div>`;
    }
    updateDashboard();
}

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
   DASHBOARD
‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
function updateDashboard() {
    if (!currentUser) return;
    const isDemo = currentAccountMode === 'demo';
    const balance = isDemo ? (currentUser.demoBalance || 25) : (currentUser.realBalance || 0);
    const profit = currentUser.totalProfit || 0;

    setEl('userName', currentUser.name || 'Trader');
    setEl('userEmail', currentUser.email || '');
    setEl('accountTypeLabel', isDemo ? 'DEMO' : 'REAL');
    setEl('dashBalance', '$' + balance.toFixed(2));
    setEl('dashAvailable', '$' + balance.toFixed(2));
    setEl('dashInTrades', '$0.00');
    setEl('dashProfit', (profit >= 0 ? '+$' : '-$') + Math.abs(profit).toFixed(2));
}

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
   AUTH ‚Äî SIGNUP
‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
function handleSignup(e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    const name     = document.getElementById('signupName').value.trim();
    const email    = document.getElementById('signupEmail').value.trim();
    const phone    = document.getElementById('signupPhone').value.trim();
    const password = document.getElementById('signupPassword').value;
    const confirm  = document.getElementById('signupConfirm').value;
    const refCode  = document.getElementById('signupReferralCode').value.trim();
    const alertEl  = document.getElementById('signupAlert');

    function showAlert(msg, type) {
        alertEl.textContent = msg;
        alertEl.className = `alert alert-${type} show`;
        setTimeout(() => alertEl.classList.remove('show'), 5000);
    }

    if (password !== confirm) { showAlert('‚ùå Passwords do not match!', 'error'); return false; }
    if (password.length < 6)  { showAlert('‚ùå Password must be at least 6 characters.', 'error'); return false; }

    const existingUsers = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('cryptoproUsers') || '[]');
    if (existingUsers.find(u => u.email === email)) { showAlert('‚ùå Email already registered. Please login.', 'error'); return false; }

    const userId = 'CP' + Date.now().toString(36).toUpperCase();
    const newUser = {
        id: userId, name, email, phone, password,
        demoBalance: 25, realBalance: 0, totalProfit: 0,
        referralCode: userId, referredBy: refCode || null,
        referrals: [], totalCommission: 0, shareCount: 0, shareEarnings: 0,
        tradeHistory: [], memberSince: new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', year: 'numeric' })
    };

    existingUsers.push(newUser);
    localStorage.setItem('cryptoproUsers', JSON.stringify(existingUsers));

    // Credit referrer
    if (refCode) {
        const referrer = existingUsers.find(u => u.referralCode === refCode || u.id === refCode);
        if (referrer) {
            referrer.referrals = referrer.referrals || [];
            referrer.referrals.push({ name, email, joinDate: new Date().toLocaleDateString() });
            localStorage.setItem('cryptoproUsers', JSON.stringify(existingUsers));
        }
    }

    currentUser = newUser;
    localStorage.setItem('cryptoproUser', JSON.stringify(newUser));

    launchConfetti();
    showAlert('üéâ Account created! Welcome to CryptoPro!', 'success');
    setTimeout(() => {
        showLayer('dashboardLayer');
        showToast(`üéâ Welcome ${name}!\n\n‚úÖ $25 Demo Bonus Credited!\nüíé Start trading or deposit to go live!`);
        addNotification('üéâ Welcome Bonus Credited', '$25 demo bonus added to your account');
    }, 1200);

    return false;
}

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
   AUTH ‚Äî LOGIN
‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
function handleLogin(e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    const email    = document.getElementById('loginEmail').value.trim();
    const password = document.getElementById('loginPassword').value;
    const alertEl  = document.getElementById('loginAlert');

    function showAlert(msg, type) {
        alertEl.textContent = msg;
        alertEl.className = `alert alert-${type} show`;
        setTimeout(() => alertEl.classList.remove('show'), 5000);
    }

    const users = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('cryptoproUsers') || '[]');
    const user  = users.find(u => u.email === email && u.password === password);

    if (!user) { showAlert('‚ùå Invalid email or password. Please try again.', 'error'); return false; }

    currentUser = user;
    localStorage.setItem('cryptoproUser', JSON.stringify(user));

    showAlert('‚úÖ Login successful! Redirecting...', 'success');
    setTimeout(() => {
        showLayer('dashboardLayer');
        showToast(`üëã Welcome back, ${user.name}!\n\nüí∞ Balance: $${(user.realBalance || 0).toFixed(2)}`);
    }, 800);

    return false;
}

function handleLogout() {
    currentUser = null;
    activeBots.clear();
    localStorage.removeItem('cryptoproUser');
    showLayer('welcomeLayer');
    showToast('üëã Logged out successfully. See you soon!');
}

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
   DEPOSIT
‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
function selectPaymentMethod(method, btn) {
    selectedPaymentMethod = method;
    document.querySelectorAll('.payment-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
    btn.classList.add('active');
    document.querySelectorAll('.payment-details').forEach(d => d.classList.remove('active'));
    const detail = document.getElementById(method);
    if (detail) detail.classList.add('active');
    updateCurrencyConversion();
}

function updateCurrencyConversion() {
    const amount = parseFloat(document.getElementById('depositAmount')?.value) || 0;
    const container = document.getElementById('currencyConverterContainer');
    if (!container || amount <= 0) { if (container) container.innerHTML = ''; return; }

    const kesAmount  = (amount * userLocation.rate).toFixed(0);
    const usdtAmount = amount.toFixed(2);

    container.innerHTML = `
        <div style="background:rgba(252,213,53,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(252,213,53,0.2);border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px;margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;">
            <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);">üí± Amount in KES</div>
            <div style="font-size:20px;font-weight:900;color:var(--accent-yellow);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;">KES ${parseInt(kesAmount).toLocaleString()}</div>
            <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);">‚âà USDT</div>
            <div style="font-size:20px;font-weight:900;color:var(--accent-green);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;">${usdtAmount} USDT</div>
        </div>`;
}

function processDeposit(e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    if (!currentUser) { showToast('Please login first!'); return false; }

    const amount = parseFloat(document.getElementById('depositAmount').value);
    const proof  = document.getElementById('depositProof').value.trim();

    if (!selectedPaymentMethod) { showToast('‚ö†Ô∏è Please select a payment method!'); return false; }
    if (amount < 10)            { showToast('‚ö†Ô∏è Minimum deposit is $10!'); return false; }
    if (!proof)                 { showToast('‚ö†Ô∏è Please provide your payment proof / transaction code.'); return false; }

    const progressBar = document.getElementById('depositProgressBar');
    const fill        = document.getElementById('progressFill');
    const label       = document.getElementById('progressLabel');
    const text        = document.getElementById('progressText');

    progressBar.classList.add('show');
    document.getElementById('depositForm').style.opacity = '0.5';
    document.getElementById('depositForm').style.pointerEvents = 'none';

    const steps = [
        { pct: 20, msg: 'üîç Verifying transaction code...' },
        { pct: 45, msg: 'üì° Connecting to payment network...' },
        { pct: 70, msg: '‚úÖ Transaction confirmed...' },
        { pct: 90, msg: 'üí∞ Crediting your account...' },
        { pct: 100, msg: 'üéâ Deposit successful!' }
    ];

    let step = 0;
    const interval = setInterval(() => {
        if (step >= steps.length) {
            clearInterval(interval);

            // Credit balance
            const bonus = (currentUser.realBalance === 0 && currentUser.totalDeposited === undefined) ? amount : 0;
            currentUser.realBalance      = (currentUser.realBalance || 0) + amount + bonus;
            currentUser.totalDeposited   = (currentUser.totalDeposited || 0) + amount;

            // Credit referrer commission
            if (currentUser.referredBy) {
                const users    = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('cryptoproUsers') || '[]');
                const referrer = users.find(u => u.referralCode === currentUser.referredBy || u.id === currentUser.referredBy);
                if (referrer) {
                    const commission = amount * 0.10;
                    referrer.realBalance    = (referrer.realBalance || 0) + commission;
                    referrer.totalCommission = (referrer.totalCommission || 0) + commission;
                    const idx = users.findIndex(u => u.id === referrer.id);
                    if (idx !== -1) users[idx] = referrer;
                    localStorage.setItem('cryptoproUsers', JSON.stringify(users));
                }
            }

            // Persist
            const users = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('cryptoproUsers') || '[]');
            const idx   = users.findIndex(u => u.id === currentUser.id);
            if (idx !== -1) users[idx] = currentUser;
            localStorage.setItem('cryptoproUsers', JSON.stringify(users));
            localStorage.setItem('cryptoproUser', JSON.stringify(currentUser));

            document.getElementById('depositForm').style.opacity = '';
            document.getElementById('depositForm').style.pointerEvents = '';
            progressBar.classList.remove('show');

            launchConfetti();
            const msg = bonus > 0
                ? `üéâ DEPOSIT SUCCESSFUL!\n\nüí∞ Deposited: $${amount.toFixed(2)}\nüéÅ Welcome Bonus: +$${bonus.toFixed(2)}\n‚úÖ Total Credited: $${(amount + bonus).toFixed(2)}\n\nFunds are now in your account!`
                : `‚úÖ DEPOSIT SUCCESSFUL!\n\nüí∞ Amount: $${amount.toFixed(2)}\n\nFunds added to your account!`;
            showToast(msg);
            addNotification('üí∞ Deposit Confirmed', `$${amount.toFixed(2)} credited to your account`);
            document.getElementById('depositForm').reset();
            document.querySelectorAll('.payment-details').forEach(d => d.classList.remove('active'));
            document.querySelectorAll('.payment-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
            selectedPaymentMethod = '';
            if (document.getElementById('currencyConverterContainer')) document.getElementById('currencyConverterContainer').innerHTML = '';
            return;
        }

        const s = steps[step++];
        fill.style.width  = s.pct + '%';
        label.textContent = s.msg;
        text.textContent  = s.pct + '% complete';
    }, 1200);

    return false;
}

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
   WITHDRAWAL
‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
function updateWithdrawalPage() {
    if (!currentUser) return;
    const bal = currentUser.realBalance || 0;
    setEl('withdrawAvailable', '$' + bal.toFixed(2));
    setEl('maxWithdraw', '$' + bal.toFixed(2));
}

function selectWithdrawMethod(method, btn) {
    selectedWithdrawMethod = method;
    document.querySelectorAll('#withdrawalLayer .payment-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
    btn.classList.add('active');
    document.querySelectorAll('#withdrawalLayer .payment-details').forEach(d => d.classList.remove('active'));
    const detail = document.getElementById('withdraw-' + method);
    if (detail) detail.classList.add('active');
}

function processWithdrawal(e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    if (!currentUser) { showToast('Please login first!'); return false; }

    const amount = parseFloat(document.getElementById('withdrawAmount').value);
    const bal    = currentUser.realBalance || 0;

    if (!selectedWithdrawMethod) { showToast('‚ö†Ô∏è Please select a withdrawal method!'); return false; }
    if (amount < 50)             { showToast('‚ö†Ô∏è Minimum withdrawal is $50!'); return false; }
    if (amount > bal)            { showToast(`‚ö†Ô∏è Insufficient balance!\n\nAvailable: $${bal.toFixed(2)}`); return false; }

    const fee    = amount * 0.02;
    const payout = amount - fee;

    const progressBar = document.getElementById('withdrawProgressBar');
    const fill        = document.getElementById('withdrawProgressFill');
    const label       = document.getElementById('withdrawProgressLabel');
    const text        = document.getElementById('withdrawProgressText');

    progressBar.classList.add('show');

    const steps = [
        { pct: 25,  msg: 'üîê Verifying account security...' },
        { pct: 55,  msg: 'üí∏ Processing withdrawal request...' },
        { pct: 80,  msg: 'üì° Sending to payment network...' },
        { pct: 100, msg: '‚úÖ Withdrawal submitted!' }
    ];

    let step = 0;
    const interval = setInterval(() => {
        if (step >= steps.length) {
            clearInterval(interval);

            currentUser.realBalance = bal - amount;
            const users = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('cryptoproUsers') || '[]');
            const idx   = users.findIndex(u => u.id === currentUser.id);
            if (idx !== -1) users[idx] = currentUser;
            localStorage.setItem('cryptoproUsers', JSON.stringify(users));
            localStorage.setItem('cryptoproUser', JSON.stringify(currentUser));

            progressBar.classList.remove('show');
            showToast(`‚úÖ WITHDRAWAL SUBMITTED!\n\nüí∏ Amount: $${amount.toFixed(2)}\nüí≥ Fee (2%): -$${fee.toFixed(2)}\nüí∞ You Receive: $${payout.toFixed(2)}\n\n‚è± Processing: 5‚Äì30 minutes\nüì± You'll receive a confirmation shortly!`);
            addNotification('üí∏ Withdrawal Processing', `$${payout.toFixed(2)} being sent to your account`);
            document.getElementById('withdrawalForm').reset();
            document.querySelectorAll('#withdrawalLayer .payment-details').forEach(d => d.classList.remove('active'));
            document.querySelectorAll('#withdrawalLayer .payment-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
            selectedWithdrawMethod = '';
            updateWithdrawalPage();
            return;
        }

        const s = steps[step++];
        fill.style.width  = s.pct + '%';
        label.textContent = s.msg;
        text.textContent  = s.pct + '% complete';
    }, 1000);

    return false;
}

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
   TRADING
‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
function executeTrade(e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    if (!currentUser) { showToast('Please login first!'); return false; }

    const amount   = parseFloat(document.getElementById('tradeAmount').value);
    const leverage = parseFloat(document.getElementById('tradeLeverage').value) || 1;
    const tp       = parseFloat(document.getElementById('takeProfitPrice').value) || 0;
    const sl       = parseFloat(document.getElementById('stopLossPrice').value) || 0;
    const bal      = currentAccountMode === 'demo' ? (currentUser.demoBalance || 0) : (currentUser.realBalance || 0);

    if (amount < 10)     { showToast('‚ö†Ô∏è Minimum trade amount is $10!'); return false; }
    if (amount > bal)    { showToast(`‚ö†Ô∏è Insufficient ${currentAccountMode} balance!\n\nAvailable: $${bal.toFixed(2)}`); return false; }

    const positionSize = amount * leverage;
    const duration     = Math.floor(Math.random() * 20000 + 10000);
    const isWin        = Math.random() < 0.62;
    const pnlPct       = (Math.random() * 0.035 + 0.008) * (isWin ? 1 : -1);
    const profit       = positionSize * pnlPct;

    showToast(`‚ö° Trade Opened!\n\n${selectedTradeType === 'buy' ? 'üìà LONG' : 'üìâ SHORT'} ${currentTradePairLabel}\nüí∞ Amount: $${amount.toFixed(2)}\n‚ö° Leverage: ${leverage}x\nüìä Position: $${positionSize.toFixed(2)}\n\n‚è≥ Closing in ~${Math.round(duration / 1000)}s...`);

    document.getElementById('tradeSubmitBtn').disabled   = true;
    document.getElementById('tradeSubmitBtn').textContent = '‚è≥ Trade Running...';

    setTimeout(() => {
        if (currentAccountMode === 'demo') currentUser.demoBalance = (currentUser.demoBalance || 0) + profit;
        else                               currentUser.realBalance  = (currentUser.realBalance  || 0) + profit;
        currentUser.totalProfit = (currentUser.totalProfit || 0) + profit;

        // Save to history
        currentUser.tradeHistory = currentUser.tradeHistory || [];
        currentUser.tradeHistory.unshift({
            id: 'TRD' + Date.now().toString(36).toUpperCase(),
            pair: currentTradePairLabel, type: selectedTradeType.toUpperCase(),
            amount, leverage, position: positionSize,
            entryPrice: currentBTCPrice, profit, isWin,
            date: new Date().toLocaleString(), mode: currentAccountMode
        });
        if (currentUser.tradeHistory.length > 100) currentUser.tradeHistory.pop();

        const users = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('cryptoproUsers') || '[]');
        const idx   = users.findIndex(u => u.id === currentUser.id);
        if (idx !== -1) users[idx] = currentUser;
        localStorage.setItem('cryptoproUsers', JSON.stringify(users));
        localStorage.setItem('cryptoproUser', JSON.stringify(currentUser));

        document.getElementById('tradeSubmitBtn').disabled   = false;
        selectTradeType(selectedTradeType);

        if (isWin) {
            launchConfetti();
            showToast(`üéâ TRADE WON!\n\n${selectedTradeType === 'buy' ? 'üìà LONG' : 'üìâ SHORT'} ${currentTradePairLabel}\n\n‚úÖ PROFIT: +$${profit.toFixed(2)}\nüí∞ New Balance: $${(currentAccountMode === 'demo' ? currentUser.demoBalance : currentUser.realBalance).toFixed(2)}`);
        } else {
            showToast(`‚ùå Trade Closed at Loss\n\n${currentTradePairLabel} moved against you\n\nüìâ LOSS: -$${Math.abs(profit).toFixed(2)}\nüí∞ New Balance: $${(currentAccountMode === 'demo' ? currentUser.demoBalance : currentUser.realBalance).toFixed(2)}\n\nüí° Tip: Try a different strategy!`, true);
        }

        addNotification(`${isWin ? 'üéâ' : 'üìâ'} Trade Closed`, `${currentTradePairLabel} ${isWin ? '+' : ''}$${profit.toFixed(2)}`);
        if (currentLayer === 'dashboardLayer') updateDashboard();
    }, duration);

    document.getElementById('tradeForm').reset();
    updatePositionSize();
    return false;
}

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
   TRADE HISTORY
‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
function generateTradeHistory() {
    const container = document.getElementById('tradeHistoryContainer');
    const statsGrid = document.getElementById('historyStatsGrid');
    if (!container || !currentUser) return;

    const history = currentUser.tradeHistory || [];

    if (history.length === 0) {
        container.innerHTML = `<div style="text-align:center;padding:60px 20px;color:var(--text-secondary);"><div style="font-size:48px;margin-bottom:12px;">üìä</div><div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;">No trades yet</div><div style="font-size:13px;margin-top:6px;">Your trade history will appear here</div></div>`;
    } else {
        container.innerHTML = history.map(t => `
            <div class="history-item">
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:10px;">
                    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;">
                        <div style="width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:10px;background:${t.isWin ? 'var(--accent-green-dim)' : 'var(--accent-red-dim)'};display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:18px;">${t.isWin ? '‚úÖ' : '‚ùå'}</div>
                        <div>
                            <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;">${t.pair} ‚Äî ${t.type}</div>
                            <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-secondary);">${t.date} ¬∑ ${t.mode.toUpperCase()}</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="text-align:right;">
                        <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:900;color:${t.profit >= 0 ? 'var(--accent-green)' : 'var(--accent-red)'};font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;">${t.profit >= 0 ? '+' : ''}$${t.profit.toFixed(2)}</div>
                        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-secondary);">${t.leverage}x leverage</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:8px;">
                    <div style="background:rgba(0,0,0,0.3);padding:8px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;">
                        <div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--text-muted);text-transform:uppercase;">Amount</div>
                        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;">$${t.amount.toFixed(2)}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background:rgba(0,0,0,0.3);padding:8px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;">
                        <div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--text-muted);text-transform:uppercase;">Position</div>
                        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;">$${t.position.toFixed(2)}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background:rgba(0,0,0,0.3);padding:8px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;">
                        <div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--text-muted);text-transform:uppercase;">Entry</div>
                        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;">$${t.entryPrice.toFixed(0)}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>`).join('');
    }

    const wins     = history.filter(t => t.isWin).length;
    const losses   = history.length - wins;
    const totalPnl = history.reduce((s, t) => s + t.profit, 0);
    const winRate  = history.length > 0 ? ((wins / history.length) * 100).toFixed(1) : '0.0';

    if (statsGrid) {
        statsGrid.innerHTML = [
            { icon: 'üìä', value: history.length, label: 'Total Trades' },
            { icon: '‚úÖ', value: wins, label: 'Winning Trades' },
            { icon: '‚ùå', value: losses, label: 'Losing Trades' },
            { icon: 'üéØ', value: winRate + '%', label: 'Win Rate' },
            { icon: 'üí∞', value: (totalPnl >= 0 ? '+$' : '-$') + Math.abs(totalPnl).toFixed(2), label: 'Total P&L' },
            { icon: '‚ö°', value: history.length > 0 ? '$' + (history.reduce((s,t)=>s+t.amount,0)/history.length).toFixed(2) : '$0', label: 'Avg Trade' }
        ].map(s => `<div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-icon">${s.icon}</div><div class="stat-value" style="font-size:22px;">${s.value}</div><div class="stat-label">${s.label}</div></div>`).join('');
    }
}

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
   REFERRAL
‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
function updateReferralPage() {
    if (!currentUser) return;
    const baseUrl = window.location.origin + window.location.pathname;
    const link    = `${baseUrl}?ref=${currentUser.referralCode || currentUser.id}`;
    setEl('referralLink', link);

    const refs  = currentUser.referrals || [];
    const comm  = currentUser.totalCommission || 0;
    const actv  = refs.length;
    const shares = currentUser.shareCount || 0;
    const shareEarnings = currentUser.shareEarnings || 0;

    setEl('totalReferrals', refs.length);
    setEl('totalCommission', '$' + comm.toFixed(2));
    setEl('activeReferrals', actv);
    setEl('totalShares', shares);
    setEl('shareCountDisplay', shares);
    setEl('shareEarningsDisplay', '$' + shareEarnings.toFixed(2));
}

function copyReferralLink() {
    if (!currentUser) return;
    const baseUrl = window.location.origin + window.location.pathname;
    const link    = `${baseUrl}?ref=${currentUser.referralCode || currentUser.id}`;
    copyToClipboard(link);
    showToast('üìã Referral link copied!\n\nShare it to earn 10% commission on all deposits!');
}

function recordShare(platform) {
    if (!currentUser) return;
    currentUser.shareCount    = (currentUser.shareCount || 0) + 1;
    currentUser.shareEarnings = (currentUser.shareEarnings || 0) + 5;
    currentUser.realBalance   = (currentUser.realBalance || 0) + 5;

    const users = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('cryptoproUsers') || '[]');
    const idx   = users.findIndex(u => u.id === currentUser.id);
    if (idx !== -1) users[idx] = currentUser;
    localStorage.setItem('cryptoproUsers', JSON.stringify(users));
    localStorage.setItem('cryptoproUser', JSON.stringify(currentUser));

    launchConfetti();
    updateReferralPage();
    showToast(`üéâ +$5 Share Bonus!\n\nThanks for sharing on ${platform}!\nüí∞ $5 credited to your real balance.\n\nKeep sharing to earn more!`);
    addNotification('üéÅ Share Bonus!', `+$5 credited for sharing on ${platform}`);
}

function shareViaWhatsApp() {
    if (!currentUser) { showToast('Please login first!'); return; }
    const baseUrl = window.location.origin + window.location.pathname;
    const link    = `${baseUrl}?ref=${currentUser.referralCode || currentUser.id}`;
    const msg     = encodeURIComponent(`üöÄ I'm making real money on CryptoPro ‚Äî the #1 AI crypto trading platform!\n\nüí∞ Get $25 FREE bonus when you sign up!\nüìà AI bots trade 24/7 automatically\nüí∏ Withdraw anytime, fast payouts\n\nüëâ Join me here: ${link}`);
    window.open(`https://wa.me/?text=${msg}`, '_blank');
    setTimeout(() => recordShare('WhatsApp'), 1000);
}

