/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
   PROFILE
‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
function populateProfileForm() {
    if (!currentUser) return;
    const f = (id, val) => { const el = document.getElementById(id); if (el) el.value = val || ''; };
    f('profileName', currentUser.name);
    f('profileEmail', currentUser.email);
    f('profilePhone', currentUser.phone);
    setEl('accountId', currentUser.id || '‚Äî');
    setEl('memberSince', currentUser.memberSince || '‚Äî');
}

function updateProfile(e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    if (!currentUser) return false;

    const newName     = document.getElementById('profileName').value.trim();
    const newEmail    = document.getElementById('profileEmail').value.trim();
    const newPhone    = document.getElementById('profilePhone').value.trim();
    const curPass     = document.getElementById('profileCurrentPassword').value;
    const newPass     = document.getElementById('profileNewPassword').value;

    if (curPass && curPass !== currentUser.password) {
        showToast('‚ùå Current password is incorrect!', true);
        return false;
    }

    currentUser.name  = newName;
    currentUser.email = newEmail;
    currentUser.phone = newPhone;
    if (newPass) currentUser.password = newPass;

    const users = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('cryptoproUsers') || '[]');
    const idx   = users.findIndex(u => u.id === currentUser.id);
    if (idx !== -1) users[idx] = currentUser;
    localStorage.setItem('cryptoproUsers', JSON.stringify(users));
    localStorage.setItem('cryptoproUser', JSON.stringify(currentUser));

    setEl('userName', newName);
    showToast('‚úÖ Profile updated successfully!');
    document.getElementById('profileCurrentPassword').value = '';
    document.getElementById('profileNewPassword').value     = '';
    return false;
}

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
   REFERRAL CODE CHECK ON LOAD
‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
function checkReferralCode() {
    const params = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
    const ref    = params.get('ref');
    if (!ref) return;

    const banner    = document.getElementById('referralSuccessBanner');
    const nameEl    = document.getElementById('referrerName');
    const refInput  = document.getElementById('signupReferralCode');

    const users    = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('cryptoproUsers') || '[]');
    const referrer = users.find(u => u.referralCode === ref || u.id === ref);

    if (banner) {
        if (referrer && nameEl) nameEl.textContent = referrer.name + "'s friend";
        banner.classList.add('show');
        setTimeout(() => closeReferralBanner(), 8000);
    }

    if (refInput) refInput.value = ref;
}

function closeReferralBanner() {
    const banner = document.getElementById('referralSuccessBanner');
    if (banner) banner.classList.remove('show');
}

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
   DETECT USER LOCATION
‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
function detectUserLocation() {
    // Lightweight heuristic ‚Äî can be replaced with a real IP-geo API call
    userLocation = { country: 'Kenya', currency: 'KES', rate: 130, city: 'Nairobi' };
}

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
   NOTIFICATIONS
‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
function renderNotifications() {
    const list     = document.getElementById('notifList');
    const countEl  = document.getElementById('notifCount');
    if (!list) return;

    const unread = notifications.filter(n => n.unread).length;
    if (countEl) { countEl.textContent = unread; countEl.style.display = unread > 0 ? 'flex' : 'none'; }

    list.innerHTML = notifications.length === 0
        ? `<div style="padding:20px;text-align:center;color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:13px;">No notifications</div>`
        : notifications.map((n, i) => `
            <div class="notif-item ${n.unread ? 'unread' : ''}" onclick="markNotifRead(${i})" style="${n.unread ? 'border-left:3px solid var(--accent-green);' : ''}">
                <div class="notif-item-title">${n.title}</div>
                <div class="notif-item-desc">${n.desc}</div>
                <div class="notif-item-time">${n.time}</div>
            </div>`).join('');
}

function addNotification(title, desc) {
    notifications.unshift({ title, desc, time: 'Just now', unread: true });
    if (notifications.length > 20) notifications.pop();
    renderNotifications();
}

function markNotifRead(idx) {
    if (notifications[idx]) notifications[idx].unread = false;
    renderNotifications();
}

function clearNotifications() {
    notifications.forEach(n => n.unread = false);
    renderNotifications();
    document.getElementById('notifDropdown')?.classList.remove('open');
}

function toggleNotifications() {
    const dropdown = document.getElementById('notifDropdown');
    if (!dropdown) return;
    dropdown.classList.toggle('open');
    if (dropdown.classList.contains('open')) {
        renderNotifications();
        document.addEventListener('click', closeNotifOnOutsideClick);
    }
}

function closeNotifOnOutsideClick(e) {
    const wrapper = document.getElementById('notifBellWrapper');
    if (wrapper && !wrapper.contains(e.target)) {
        document.getElementById('notifDropdown')?.classList.remove('open');
        document.removeEventListener('click', closeNotifOnOutsideClick);
    }
}

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
   AI ASSISTANT (ARIA)
‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
const ARIA_RESPONSES = {
    'best bot':        'ü§ñ For beginners, I recommend **Scalper Pro** ‚Äî it only needs $10 minimum and has an 87% win rate with 50+ trades/day!\n\nFor larger balances, **Arbitrage AI** has the highest returns at 91% win rate.',
